      # The notification system

      Options:

      * `title` - modal window title
      * `okLabelText` - modal dismiss button text
      * `triggerLabelText` - launch button text

      Sub-divisions:

      * One or more `.previews`
      * One or more `.triggers`

      Sampe code:

      ```
        +exercise-modal({name: 'ex98_1', title: 'Full screen hello', okLabelText: 'Done', triggerLabelText: 'How are you?'})
          +yesno
            p Are you ok?


        +exercise-modal({name: 'ex98_2',
          title: 'Sample with preview div', 
          okLabelText: 'Done',
          triggerLabelText: 'Who sings that?'})
          .preview
            p
            | Iarba ce-a rămas verde într-un cucui

          +textline({name: 'ex98_2_1'})

        +exercise-modal({name: 'ex98_1', title: 'Full screen hello', okLabelText: 'Done', triggerLabelText: 'How are you?'})
          .preview
            p Custom trigger!
              span.trigger Click this absolutely unconspicous text!
          +yesno
            p You din't see that coming.
      ```

